'''Contemporary commercial music''' or '''CCM''' is a term used by some [[vocal pedagogists]] in the [[United States of America]] to refer to non-classical [[music]]. This term encompasses [[jazz]], [[pop music|pop]], [[blues]], [[soul music|soul]], [[country music|country]], [[Folk music|folk]], and [[Rock music|rock]] styles.<ref>[http://www.speech.kth.se/prod/publications/files/3003.pdf Kappan<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref>
